Export_ExportAuditEventsWSRequest.description: Request object for exporting audit events to CSV format with filtering options.

endInterval.description: End time interval in milliseconds for filtering audit events

excludeActions.description: If not empty, events with actions specified in the list are filtered out. If both include and exclude actions are specified, exclude actions are ignored.

items.description: If not empty, events with actions specified in the list are filtered out. If both include and exclude actions are specified, exclude actions are ignored.

includeActions.description: If not empty, only events with actions specified in the list are included. If both include and exclude actions are specified, exclude actions are ignored.

items.description: If not empty, only events with actions specified in the list are included. If both include and exclude actions are specified, exclude actions are ignored.

startInterval.description: Start time interval in milliseconds for filtering audit events

Vehicle_GetVehicleEventsWSRequest.description: Request object for getting vehicle events with filters and additive queries.

deviceUuidFilter.description: Filter events by specific reporting device uuids

items.description: RUUID with optional appended facet information

endTimeMs.description: Time window filter end (newest) time in Epoch milliseconds

licensePlateExactQuery.description: Query events by exact license plate number. Query fields are additive queries (returned events satisfy at least one of the query fields)

items.description: Query events by exact license plate number. Query fields are additive queries (returned events satisfy at least one of the query fields)

licensePlateFuzzyQuery.description: Query events by partial or complete license plate with fuzzy character matching. Query fields are additive queries (returned events satisfy at least one of the query fields)

locationUuidFilter.description: Filter events by specific reporting location uuids

nameQuery.description: Query events by vehicle name. Query fields are additive queries (returned events satisfy at least one of the query fields)

items.description: Query events by vehicle name. Query fields are additive queries (returned events satisfy at least one of the query fields)

startTimeMs.description: Time window filter start (oldest) time in Epoch milliseconds

unnamedQuery.description: Query events by name presence.  If false, returns events with a name.  If true, returns events without names.  Omit if not needed.  Query fields are additive queries (returned events satisfy at least one of the query fields)

vehicleLabelQuery.description: Query events by vehicle labels. Query fields are additive queries (returned events satisfy at least one of the query fields)

items.description: Query events by vehicle labels. Query fields are additive queries (returned events satisfy at least one of the query fields)
